      <b data-is-speakable>Sanders Could Be The First Jewish President, But He Doesn't Like To Talk About It </b>   <b data-is-speakable>Bernie Sanders isn't into identity politics. He says he's "proud to be Jewish" but "not particularly religious."</b>
